result.name: PizzaExpress Taikoo Shing

reviews.text: Amazing food, so many options. great with kids too. The lava is my favorite pizza, I like their pasta too. It's easy to keep the kids full and entertained. Come hungry the kids menu is a lot of food

Small space...venue was booked for a party but the food was quick and our server was pretty good/attentive. Recommended the soup/starters as well as as dessert at the end. Pizza's as every other Pizza express. Tried their Wheat Ale (brewed by Pizza express as claimed), decent beer but not one of the best I had.

Pizza express is always decent enough. Their "Hawaii" pizza, which is a combination I normally steer very clear of as I absolutely despise it, was surprisingly good (it was the bianchi version without tomato sauce). This particular pizza express wasn't among the better, having a relatively small seating space with narrow passages (L shape), so wasn't the best ambience.
I love pasta
